        <h2 class="left-heading destination-section-heading">Ciutadella Park</h2>
        <p>East of the Gothic Quarter is Barcelona's <strong>Ciutadella Park</strong>, where you'll find the magnificent Cascada Monumental, a gorgeous neoclassical fountain and monument. The park also contains many sculptures and gardens, the elegant Palace of Parliament, the city's zoo, and the impressive Castle of the Three Dragons, which houses a zoological museum.</p>
        <p>On the northeastern side of the park is a connected walkway leading to the grand <strong>Arco de Triunfo de Barcelona</strong>, a striking triumphal arch.</p>
    </section>


