        <p>Several blocks north of La Sagrada Familia is an incredible UNESCO listed modernisme complex, the <strong>Hospital de la Santa Creu i Sant Pau</strong>. Although this beautiful complex of buildings once served as a hospital, it now exists as a vast museum and cultural center. The complex's extravagant exteriors are strikingly gorgeous.</p>
